Package com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.collection

Interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Indexable>

  • Type Parameters:
    ResourceT - the top level Azure resource type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActionGroups, ActiveDirectoryApplications, ApplicationGateways, AvailabilitySets, BatchAccounts, BatchAIClusters, BatchAIFileServers, CdnProfiles, ContainerGroups, ContainerServices, CosmosDBAccounts, DiagnosticSettings, Disks, DnsZones, EventHubNamespaces, ExpressRouteCircuits, Identities, KubernetesClusters, LoadBalancers, ManagementLocks, NetworkInterfaces, NetworkPeerings, Networks, NetworkSecurityGroups, NetworkWatchers, PublicIPAddresses, RedisCaches, Registries, ResourceGroups, RoleAssignments, RouteTables, SearchServices, ServiceBusNamespaces, Snapshots, SqlServers, StorageAccounts, TrafficManagerProfiles, VirtualMachineCustomImages, VirtualMachines, VirtualMachineScaleSets, VirtualNetworkGateways

    public interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Indexable>
    Providing access to creating a batch of Azure top level resources of same type.

    (Note: this interface is not intended to be implemented by user code)
